with Irinyan this evening?

00:03:58.113 --> 00:04:00.073 position:50% align:center
Uh, well...

00:04:00.156 --> 00:04:02.575 position:50% align:center
I'm not sure,
maybe she's just tired.

00:04:02.659 --> 00:04:05.036 position:50% align:center
[ANYA]
I've never seen her like this.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:06.955 position:50% align:center
I'm worried about her, Lev.

00:04:07.038 --> 00:04:08.456 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:04:19.092 --> 00:04:20.260 position:50% align:center
Are you gonna eat?

00:04:20.343 --> 00:04:22.887 position:50% align:center
Of course. I was
just taking my time.

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:26.641 position:50% align:center
[gasps, groans]

00:04:27.726 --> 00:04:30.061 position:50% align:center
Whoa! Hey!

00:04:30.145 --> 00:04:31.938 position:50% align:center
That's not good.

00:04:34.107 --> 00:04:39.112 position:50% align:center
[NATALIA]
Hm?

00:04:39.195 --> 00:04:42.490 position:50% align:center
--[IRINA groans]
--[buzzing]

00:04:44.492 --> 00:04:49.164 position:50% align:center
[IRINA pants]

00:04:49.247 --> 00:04:50.081 position:50% align:center
[LEV]
You okay?

00:04:50.165 --> 00:04:51.374 position:50% align:center
[IRINA]
Yeah.

00:04:54.711 --> 00:04:56.129 position:50% align:center
[SAGALEVICH]
That's more like it!

00:04:56.212 --> 00:04:58.006 position:50% align:center
If the subject isn't being
pushed to the brink of death,

00:04:58.089 --> 00:04:59.924 position:50% align:center
then we're doing
something wrong!

00:05:00.008 --> 00:05:00.759 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]

00:05:00.842 --> 00:05:05.055 position:50% align:center
[pants]

00:05:05.138 --> 00:05:07.182 position:50% align:center
